http://www.sublimetext.com/


descargar nasm:
http://www.nasm.us/pub/nasm/releasebuilds/2.11.06/nasm-2.11.06.tar.bz2

comandos para instalar nasm 
$ sudo sh autogen.sh

Then run configure to detect your platform settings and generate makefiles.

$ sh configure



$ make



$ make strip



$ make install

